Title: Page 2
Description.note: Notes from the scribe:ወኀበ ተነበ ዝንቱ መጽሐፍ ይሰደዱ መናፍስት ርኩሳን ወኲሉ ደዌ ወሕማም ወይሠዓር ሥራይ ወይደመሰስ ከመ ጢስ ዘቅድመ ገጸ እሳት በኃይለ ሎኢ ኤሎኢ ኤላኢ ወኀበ ሀሎ ዝንቱ መጽሐፍ ይከውን ሣህል ወምሕረት እስከ ለዓለመ ዓለም አሜን ; "When this book is read, unclean spirits and all disease and sickness will flee. Magic will be disempowered and destroyed like smoke from the fire, by the power of Lo'e, a Lo'e, a La'e. Where ever this book is will be forgiveness and mercy forever and ever amen."|~|Prayer against the snake.
